item.title: Problem! help!
item.dc:creator: @bburton31 bburton31
item.description:
@bburton31 wrote:

or it doesn’t know the directory to find jdk 6.0, try re-nameing your “jdk1.6.0_01” to “jdk1.6.0”, that should work if not tell me and you could try using The perfect compiler v1.9 if you haven’t already do a search for it. Hope it helps

that’s a simpler noob friendly method. Which i used lol.

btw: try a few different compilers from different sources!!! because on some i still get that error but on others i don’t prob because they’re out of date but i suggest you try different compiler too!
